name: Heelt
content: Heelt was a Gran male criminal who operated during the reign of the Galactic Empire. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, Heelt stole a silvercore speeder from Boss Gyuti of the Black Sun criminal syndicate, which he intended to sell to two Snivvians. When Heelt met with the two in Ord Mantell City on the planet Ord Mantell, he presented the speeder to them and let them inspect the vehicle. As Snivvians looked at the speeder, the crew of the Ubese bounty hunter Boushh arrived to recover it for Gyuti and killed all present.
